dev-1.x.name: drupal/mimeinfo

security-coverage.message: Dev releases are not covered by Drupal security advisories.

dev-1.x.description: Module provides an overrides for three basic stream wrappers - public, private and temporary. If you allow the overriding, the MIME-type of files will be determined with help of FileInfo extension, or, if it does not exist, - by binary data.

1.0.0.name: drupal/mimeinfo

security-coverage.message: Covered by Drupal's security advisory policy

1.0.0.description: Module provides an overrides for three basic stream wrappers - public, private and temporary. If you allow the overriding, the MIME-type of files will be determined with help of FileInfo extension, or, if it does not exist, - by binary data.
